<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      /* Email styles */
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
      <h1>You've been invited to join <%= @team.name %></h1>
      
      <p>You've been invited to join the <%= @team.name %> team on Candor Teams.</p>
      
      <p>Candor Teams is a platform where team members provide weekly feedback to each other, helping everyone grow together.</p>
      
      <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= claim_invites_url(token: @invite.token) %>" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
          Accept Invitation
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> This invitation will expire on <%= @expires_at %>.</p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
      
      <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;" />
      
      <p style="color: #777; font-size: 12px;">
        If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>